{
  "stem": "365.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we would make fire, because for cover, you had only a thin flannelette blanket to cover yourself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the barracks were extremely cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not insulated or anything, so we were burning fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, we had to have like a guarding the barracks, like night duty.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two prisoners had to be in the barracks, that if a prisoner had to go to the outhouse at night, one of the guards had to go with him, from the prisoners, to make sure that he returns, because one of the prisoners escaped about a month previously.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't find him anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that what they installed-- our night duty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other was still at the barracks duty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On that night, the commandant comes for inspection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He comes in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first he ask, how come there is fire going in the thing?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I report to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I says, sir, nobody gave us order that we are not supposed to have, and it's extremely cold in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Since we have the roots from the trees that we dug up at the construction site, so we had fuel, rather than to waste it, we keep warm the barracks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Were you speaking in German?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In German, or course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew German because we lived close to German border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was already three years on the German occupation, so I was already quite fluent in German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Step forward, [INAUDIBLE], they assembled all the night duties from all the barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were six barracks in that camp-- took us all into the shower stalls, into the shower room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everyone was meted out 40 lashes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of guys, mostly, I was one of the youngest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a kid at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
